And all the troubles
Melt away.

1074
00:44:14,551 --> 00:44:16,091
It's a magical place.

1075
00:44:16,087 --> 00:44:17,917
It sounds wonderful.

1076
00:44:17,922 --> 00:44:19,462
Everybody needs
Some place to escape to.

1077
00:44:19,457 --> 00:44:21,057
Exactly.

1078
00:44:21,059 --> 00:44:23,329
That's what it's like
For me out here.

1079
00:44:23,328 --> 00:44:25,728
Dinner awaits.

1080
00:44:25,730 --> 00:44:29,070
It's beautiful!

1081
00:44:29,067 --> 00:44:31,727
I didn't realize
You were such a romantic.

1082
00:44:31,736 --> 00:44:33,996
Ah, i didn't either.

1083
00:44:36,607 --> 00:44:37,937
This is delicious.

1084
00:44:37,942 --> 00:44:40,182
Mm. I can't cook
To save my life,

1085
00:44:40,178 --> 00:44:42,378
But i am fantastic
At ordering well.

1086
00:44:44,815 --> 00:44:46,975
Uh, look, there's
Something important

1087
00:44:46,985 --> 00:44:48,115
I need to tell you,

1088
00:44:48,119 --> 00:44:50,849
But i'm not really
Sure how to say it.

1089
00:44:50,855 --> 00:44:52,885
More couscous?

1090
00:44:52,891 --> 00:44:54,421
I'm fine.

1091
00:44:54,426 --> 00:44:56,056
Right.
Uh, all right, uh...

1092
00:44:56,061 --> 00:44:57,661
The thing is,

1093
00:44:57,662 --> 00:44:58,962
When we first met,

1094
00:44:58,963 --> 00:45:00,763
I didn't think things
Would progress so far.

1095
00:45:00,765 --> 00:45:02,025
Liam, wait.

1096
00:45:02,033 --> 00:45:03,233
Before
You say anything,

1097
00:45:03,234 --> 00:45:06,144
I... I have to
Tell you something.

1098
00:45:06,137 --> 00:45:07,437
I...

1099
00:45:07,439 --> 00:45:10,009
Haven't been totally
Honest with you.

1100
00:45:10,008 --> 00:45:10,968
You haven't?

1101
00:45:10,975 --> 00:45:12,775
Remember how i told you

1102
00:45:12,777 --> 00:45:14,777
I recently went
Through a bad break-up?

1103
00:45:14,779 --> 00:45:16,249
You're getting back
Together with him.

1104
00:45:16,247 --> 00:45:17,147
What?

1105
00:45:17,148 --> 00:45:18,178
No!

1106
00:45:18,183 --> 00:45:19,353
Absolutely not.

1107
00:45:19,350 --> 00:45:22,850
Never. I just...

1108
00:45:22,854 --> 00:45:24,824
The whole thing
Actually hit me

1109
00:45:24,823 --> 00:45:28,123
A lot harder
Than i admitted.

1110
00:45:28,126 --> 00:45:30,186
He was a professional
Athlete,

1111
00:45:30,195 --> 00:45:32,695
And the break-up
Was very public,

1112
00:45:32,697 --> 00:45:34,627
And...

1113
00:45:34,632 --> 00:45:37,702
Pretty humiliating,
Honestly.

1114
00:45:37,702 --> 00:45:39,472
My terrible love life
Went viral.

1115
00:45:39,471 --> 00:45:41,141
That must've been awful.

1116
00:45:41,139 --> 00:45:42,109
Yeah.

1117
00:45:42,107 --> 00:45:43,137
A word of advice--

1118
00:45:43,141 --> 00:45:44,471
Never date
A famous person.

1119
00:45:44,476 --> 00:45:47,806
I won't make
That mistake again.

1120
00:45:49,046 --> 00:45:53,016
The worst part,
Though, was that...

1121
00:45:53,017 --> 00:45:57,017
This man that
I thought i loved

1122
00:45:57,021 --> 00:46:00,021
Ended up being someone
Completely different

1123
00:46:00,024 --> 00:46:02,194
Than i thought he was.

1124
00:46:02,193 --> 00:46:05,833
I guess i just lost
My ability to trust men.

1125
00:46:06,830 --> 00:46:09,800
And so when i met you,

1126
00:46:09,801 --> 00:46:11,401
I was like,

1127
00:46:11,402 --> 00:46:14,572
"wow, too good
To be true."

1128
00:46:14,572 --> 00:46:16,642
And so i've kind of been
Giving you little tests

1129
00:46:16,641 --> 00:46:18,111
Just to prove

1130
00:46:18,109 --> 00:46:21,079
That you aren't...
Too good to be true.

1131
00:46:21,079 --> 00:46:22,209
Tests?

1132
00:46:22,213 --> 00:46:23,383
Yeah.

1133
00:46:23,381 --> 00:46:25,311
This is embarrassing.

1134
00:46:25,316 --> 00:46:28,786
I... My friends
Interrogating you.

1135
00:46:28,787 --> 00:46:30,517
Me dropping by
During your lunch

1136
00:46:30,522 --> 00:46:31,722
With your client.

1137
00:46:31,723 --> 00:46:33,293
I kind of arranged
Those things

1138
00:46:33,291 --> 00:46:35,491
Just to help myself
Make sure

1139
00:46:35,493 --> 00:46:38,393
That this was real.

1140
00:46:38,396 --> 00:46:40,296
Oh! And the girl
You met

1141
00:46:40,298 --> 00:46:42,228
In front of
My office, tabitha,

1142
00:46:42,233 --> 00:46:43,603
We actually
Work together,

1143
00:46:43,601 --> 00:46:47,571
And i overheard her
Asking you out.

1144
00:46:47,572 --> 00:46:50,072
You're the only woman
I wanted to go out with.

1145
00:46:50,074 --> 00:46:51,444
I know that now.

1146
00:46:51,442 --> 00:46:53,242
And i should've

1147
00:46:53,244 --> 00:46:55,114
Trusted it
From the beginning.

1148
00:46:55,113 --> 00:46:56,553
I'm so sorry, liam.

1149
00:46:56,548 --> 00:46:58,008
I don't know
What else to say.

1150
00:46:58,016 --> 00:47:00,046
So that's it?

1151
00:47:00,051 --> 00:47:01,881
That's what you haven't
Been honest about?

1152
00:47:01,886 --> 00:47:03,086
You hate me,
Don't you?

1153
00:47:03,087 --> 00:47:05,187
Sophie,
I don't hate you.

1154
00:47:05,190 --> 00:47:07,060
I'm falling in love
With you.

1155
00:47:17,768 --> 00:47:21,468
Okay.

1156
00:47:21,472 --> 00:47:23,612
That went better
Than i thought it would.

1157
00:47:24,575 --> 00:47:35,415
[♪♪]

1158
00:47:35,420 --> 00:47:40,020
I feel so much better
Having that out in the open.

1159
00:47:40,024 --> 00:47:45,804
I've been so nervous all
Night.

1160
00:47:45,797 --> 00:47:47,627
There was something
You wanted to say to me.

1161
00:47:47,632 --> 00:47:49,472
What? Oh. Oh, nothing.

1162
00:47:49,467 --> 00:47:50,567
Are you sure?

1163
00:47:50,568 --> 00:47:51,798
I'm so sorry.

1164
00:47:51,803 --> 00:47:53,473
I feel like i kind of
Hijacked your moment.

1165
00:47:53,471 --> 00:47:55,241
Ah, it's not important.

1166
00:47:55,240 --> 00:47:56,940
More wine?

1167
00:47:58,208 --> 00:47:59,578
Please.

1168
00:48:01,912 --> 00:48:04,482
I can't wait to see
What's for dessert.

1169
00:48:11,755 --> 00:48:13,515
What was i
Supposed to do?

1170
00:48:13,524 --> 00:48:15,464
You were supposed to
Tell her the truth.

1171
00:48:15,460 --> 00:48:16,630
Well, this athlete
She was engaged to

1172
00:48:16,628 --> 00:48:17,658
Broke her heart,

1173
00:48:17,662 --> 00:48:19,032
And half the country
Was talking about it.

1174
00:48:19,030 --> 00:48:21,130
She swore she'd never
Date a famous person again.

1175
00:48:21,132 --> 00:48:22,772
What do you think

1176
00:48:22,767 --> 00:48:24,067
She's gonna do when
She finds out who i really
Am?

1177
00:48:24,068 --> 00:48:25,298
I can't just dump
All this on her.

1178
00:48:25,303 --> 00:48:26,603
You've run out of time.

1179
00:48:26,604 --> 00:48:28,044
The reveal is tomorrow
Night.

1180
00:48:28,039 --> 00:48:29,239
Well, then,
Let's postpone it.

1181
00:48:29,240 --> 00:48:30,470
We can't.

1182
00:48:30,475 --> 00:48:31,865
Get me a meeting
With the publishers.

1183
00:48:31,876 --> 00:48:33,876
I'll find a way
To change their minds.

1184
00:48:33,878 --> 00:48:35,778
It won't be easy
To convince them, liam.

1185
00:48:35,780 --> 00:48:37,880
Well, i'll find a way
To convince them.

1186
00:48:37,882 --> 00:48:39,822
I have to.

1187
00:48:40,717 --> 00:48:42,117
They can't do that.

1188
00:48:42,120 --> 00:48:43,620
Unfortunately,
The suits call the shots,

1189
00:48:43,621 --> 00:48:45,691
And they can do
Whatever they want.

1190
00:48:45,690 --> 00:48:46,920
But just to cut
All the book reviews?

1191
00:48:46,925 --> 00:48:49,055
That-- that doesn't
Even make any sense!

1192
00:48:49,060 --> 00:48:50,960
They want more space
For video games and movies.

1193
00:48:50,962 --> 00:48:52,532
They're even making me
Create
A whole new section

1194
00:48:52,530 --> 00:48:53,930
On celebrity gossip.

1195
00:48:53,932 --> 00:48:56,832
Book reviews just don't
Have enough juice these
Days.

1196
00:48:56,834 --> 00:48:59,004
Look, i've been
A team player, phil,

1197
00:48:59,003 --> 00:49:00,603
Covering music and movies,

1198
00:49:00,605 --> 00:49:02,335
Whatever you needed,

1199
00:49:02,340 --> 00:49:04,570
But you know the book
Reviews
Are what i love.

1200
00:49:04,575 --> 00:49:06,735
That's the reason
I came to the daily.

1201
00:49:06,744 --> 00:49:09,314
What can i tell you, sophie?
It's a business.

1202
00:49:09,314 --> 00:49:12,014
Lots of people read books!

1203
00:49:12,016 --> 00:49:13,576
I mean, sure,
It's a changing industry,
But--

1204
00:49:13,584 --> 00:49:15,384
No more book reviews.

1205
00:49:15,386 --> 00:49:17,546
I wish
It was different.

1206
00:49:25,862 --> 00:49:28,732
Then i don't know
If i can stay.

1207
00:49:32,336 --> 00:49:34,836
I need to figure out
What it is i want to do.

1208
00:49:38,475 --> 00:49:41,975
Well, that's a decision
You're gonna have to make.

1209
00:49:41,980 --> 00:49:44,350
But make it quickly.
I got a paper to run.

1210
00:49:44,349 --> 00:49:47,519
[♪♪]

1211
00:49:52,322 --> 00:49:54,492
[sophie]: so you don't think
It's a stupid thing to do?

1212
00:49:54,492 --> 00:49:55,932
Not at all,
But it's a big step.

1213
00:49:55,927 --> 00:49:57,887
I'm terrified.

1214
00:49:58,962 --> 00:50:00,862
But i think it's what i
Want.

1215
00:50:00,865 --> 00:50:02,595
You were right,
That's what's important.

1216
00:50:02,600 --> 00:50:04,200
Well, it sounds
Like a good plan.

1217
00:50:04,202 --> 00:50:05,532
I'm gonna
Go with my gut.

1218
00:50:05,536 --> 00:50:07,596
I guess it worked
With you yesterday.

1219
00:50:07,605 --> 00:50:09,165
That's right.

1220
00:50:09,173 --> 00:50:10,713
Look, i-i found out

1221
00:50:10,708 --> 00:50:12,938
That i have to go to new
York
For a meeting tomorrow,

1222
00:50:12,944 --> 00:50:14,584
So i'm a little frazzled.
I fly out in a couple of
Hours.

1223
00:50:14,579 --> 00:50:16,149
Wait. New york? Why?

1224
00:50:16,147 --> 00:50:18,207
Just a contractual thing
I need to address,

1225
00:50:18,216 --> 00:50:19,776
But i have to do it
In person.

1226
00:50:19,784 --> 00:50:20,854
How long will you be gone?

1227
00:50:20,852 --> 00:50:22,182
Just overnight.
I'll be back tomorrow.

1228
00:50:22,186 --> 00:50:24,586
Well, do you think

1229
00:50:24,589 --> 00:50:26,689
You might be up for a date
Night
Tomorrow night?

1230
00:50:26,691 --> 00:50:28,791
How about an early dinner?
Say, 5:30?

1231
00:50:28,793 --> 00:50:31,893
Sure. I'm down
For the early bird special.

1232
00:50:31,896 --> 00:50:33,756
Have a safe flight.

1233
00:50:33,765 --> 00:50:36,695
Okay. Bye.

1234
00:50:36,701 --> 00:50:38,801
Bye.

1235
00:50:40,504 --> 00:50:42,104
That sounds
So romantic.

1236
00:50:42,106 --> 00:50:44,206
Dinner
By candlelight?

1237
00:50:44,208 --> 00:50:46,178
Yeah. It...it was.

1238
00:50:46,177 --> 00:50:49,047
He told me he was
Falling in love with me,

1239
00:50:49,047 --> 00:50:50,977
And then we kissed.

1240
00:50:50,982 --> 00:50:53,382
Wow!

1241
00:50:53,384 --> 00:50:56,594
And you want to know
The best part?

1242
00:50:56,587 --> 00:50:58,147
I trust him.

1243
00:50:58,156 --> 00:50:59,216
Oh yeah?

1244
00:50:59,223 --> 00:51:02,093
Not a "he passed
The test" kind of trust,

1245
00:51:02,093 --> 00:51:03,833
A trust where
I want to kick myself

1246
00:51:03,828 --> 00:51:05,998
For having ever given him
A test in the first place.

1247
00:51:05,997 --> 00:51:08,457
I never thought
I would

1248
00:51:08,466 --> 00:51:10,426
Feel like this
About someone again,

1249
00:51:10,435 --> 00:51:13,195
But he just
Keeps surprising me.

1250
00:51:13,204 --> 00:51:14,674
This is so great.

1251
00:51:14,672 --> 00:51:16,572
I'm so happy for you.

1252
00:51:16,574 --> 00:51:19,384
He's on a trip
To new york for one day,

1253
00:51:19,377 --> 00:51:21,137
And i already miss him.

1254
00:51:21,145 --> 00:51:23,405
What am i in, high school?

1255
00:51:23,414 --> 00:51:25,754
You are in love.

1256
00:51:25,750 --> 00:51:27,150
Oh.

1257
00:51:27,151 --> 00:51:30,091
Okay, enough
About my love life.

1258
00:51:30,088 --> 00:51:33,588
I have something
I want to show you.

1259
00:51:33,591 --> 00:51:34,991
I put it together
Last night,

1260
00:51:34,992 --> 00:51:38,032
And you have to promise me
That you will be nice.

1261
00:51:38,029 --> 00:51:40,159
"rivetingreads.com."

1262
00:51:40,164 --> 00:51:41,334
What is it?

1263
00:51:41,332 --> 00:51:43,172
My new business.

1264
00:51:43,167 --> 00:51:44,397
Your new business?

1265
00:51:44,402 --> 00:51:46,202
What about the paper?

1266
00:51:46,204 --> 00:51:49,414
Well, liam said something
To me the other day

1267
00:51:49,407 --> 00:51:52,367
About following
My dreams

1268
00:51:52,376 --> 00:51:53,906
And doing what
I want to do,

1269
00:51:53,911 --> 00:51:55,411
And i think this might be
It.

1270
00:51:55,413 --> 00:51:58,253
This is so fantastic.

1271
00:51:58,249 --> 00:52:00,019
I have a meeting
With my editor later,

1272
00:52:00,017 --> 00:52:01,077
And then it goes live.

1273
00:52:01,085 --> 00:52:03,245
Looks like
Liam's good for you.

1274
00:52:03,254 --> 00:52:05,554
Mm-hmm.

1275
00:52:05,556 --> 00:52:08,016
[♪♪]

1276
00:52:08,025 --> 00:52:09,885
So how are you
Holding up?

1277
00:52:09,894 --> 00:52:11,264
I'm nervous.

1278
00:52:11,262 --> 00:52:12,662
Yeah, so am i.

1279
00:52:12,663 --> 00:52:14,903
You're not supposed
To admit that to me.

1280
00:52:14,899 --> 00:52:15,999
[laughs]

1281
00:52:16,000 --> 00:52:18,430
Liam, i'm not gonna
Sugarcoat this.

1282
00:52:18,436 --> 00:52:19,696
These people are sharks.

1283
00:52:19,704 --> 00:52:21,204
And i don't even know

1284
00:52:21,205 --> 00:52:23,065
