Go through with it.

1304
00:53:07,251 --> 00:53:09,551
Just not tonight.

1305
00:53:09,554 --> 00:53:10,994
I give you my word.

1306
00:53:10,988 --> 00:53:12,718
Well, we don't really
Need your word, liam.

1307
00:53:12,723 --> 00:53:15,663
