That guarantees it.

1308
00:53:15,660 --> 00:53:16,930
Right.

1309
00:53:16,928 --> 00:53:20,558
I just need you to delay
The reveal a few more weeks.

1310
00:53:20,565 --> 00:53:22,455
Liam's not
Being unreasonable.

1311
00:53:22,466 --> 00:53:24,226
He's just asking
For more time.

1312
00:53:24,235 --> 00:53:26,735
Jackie, he has already
Canceled once.

1313
00:53:26,737 --> 00:53:29,307
This has all been timed
To the release of the new
Book.

1314
00:53:29,307 --> 00:53:30,807
We've built
A marketing approach,

1315
00:53:30,808 --> 00:53:33,878
Not to mention a substantial
Amount of effort and money,

1316
00:53:33,878 --> 00:53:36,178
Around revealing
Gabriel august's identity.

1317
00:53:36,180 --> 00:53:38,110
And obviously,
Once that happens,

1318
00:53:38,115 --> 00:53:40,575
The demands
On liam's personal life

1319
00:53:40,585 --> 00:53:41,615
Are going to be extreme.

1320
00:53:41,619 --> 00:53:43,889
I just need a few more
Weeks.

1321
00:53:43,888 --> 00:53:45,418
That's all i'm asking.

1322
00:53:45,423 --> 00:53:48,723
[♪♪]

1323
00:53:48,726 --> 00:53:50,986
Liam.

1324
00:53:50,995 --> 00:53:52,225
They won't do it.

1325
00:53:52,230 --> 00:53:53,300
I'm sorry.

1326
00:53:53,297 --> 00:53:54,897
I fought for you
In there,

1327
00:53:54,899 --> 00:53:56,429
But the machine
Is just too far along

1328
00:53:56,434 --> 00:53:57,504
For them
To stop it now.

1329
00:53:57,501 --> 00:53:58,871
The reveal
Is on for tonight.

1330
00:53:58,869 --> 00:54:01,139
I'm really starting
To hate gabriel august.

1331
00:54:01,138 --> 00:54:03,668
You need to talk to sophie.

1332
00:54:03,674 --> 00:54:06,114
I'm meeting her for dinner
Tonight at 5:30.

1333
00:54:06,110 --> 00:54:07,440
That'll be
Cutting it close.

1334
00:54:07,445 --> 00:54:09,705
-we'll make it.
-okay.

1335
00:54:12,482 --> 00:54:13,952
Okay, so are we clear

1336
00:54:13,951 --> 00:54:15,281
On the plan
For later tonight?

1337
00:54:15,286 --> 00:54:16,846
Jasper's bookloft, 7:30.

1338
00:54:16,854 --> 00:54:18,324
Actually, make it 7:00,

1339
00:54:18,322 --> 00:54:20,022
So my blood pressure
Doesn't get too high.

1340
00:54:20,024 --> 00:54:21,124
I'll be there.

1341
00:54:21,125 --> 00:54:22,685
Bad news?

1342
00:54:22,693 --> 00:54:24,533
She's got a work meeting.
She just canceled dinner.

1343
00:54:24,528 --> 00:54:25,958
-what are you gonna do?
-find her.

1344
00:54:25,963 --> 00:54:29,533
I have to tell her before
I make the announcement.

1345
00:54:29,533 --> 00:54:32,673
You call me!
Let me know how it goes.

1346
00:54:33,637 --> 00:54:35,097
[recording]: it's sophie.

1347
00:54:35,106 --> 00:54:37,466
Tell me what's on your mind
After the tone. [beep]

1348
00:54:37,475 --> 00:54:39,235
Hey, sophie.
I got your text.

1349
00:54:39,243 --> 00:54:41,743
I'm back in town.
I really need to talk to
You.

1350
00:54:41,746 --> 00:54:43,446
Like, right away,
Face-to-face,

1351
00:54:43,447 --> 00:54:47,077
So call me the second
You get this, okay?

1352
00:54:47,084 --> 00:54:49,184
I know, but if he said
It was background,

1353
00:54:49,186 --> 00:54:50,446
You got to keep
His name out of it.

1354
00:54:50,454 --> 00:54:51,924
That's journalism 101!

1355
00:54:51,922 --> 00:54:53,422
Yeah. Okay.

1356
00:54:53,424 --> 00:54:56,034
Okay, let me know
How it shakes out.

1357
00:54:56,027 --> 00:54:58,257
Sorry i couldn't
Fit you in earlier.

1358
00:54:58,262 --> 00:55:00,602
I had to keep a reporter
From getting sued.

1359
00:55:00,598 --> 00:55:02,128
What's up?

1360
00:55:02,133 --> 00:55:05,173
I wanted to let you know
That today is my last day.

1361
00:55:06,703 --> 00:55:09,243
Your last day?

1362
00:55:09,240 --> 00:55:11,110
So you're leaving the paper
?

1363
00:55:11,108 --> 00:55:14,208
I'm starting my own website.

1364
00:55:14,211 --> 00:55:16,051
One where i get to do

1365
00:55:16,047 --> 00:55:19,147
The kind of reviews
That i want to do.

1366
00:55:19,150 --> 00:55:21,720
Can you make a living
Doing that?

1367
00:55:21,719 --> 00:55:24,919
Well, it may
Take me a few months

1368
00:55:24,922 --> 00:55:28,062
To get enough advertisers,
But...

1369
00:55:28,059 --> 00:55:31,059
I'm going to give it a try.

1370
00:55:31,062 --> 00:55:33,332
Well, i hate to lose you,
Sophie,

1371
00:55:33,331 --> 00:55:35,001
But i have to admit,
I'm a little jealous.

1372
00:55:34,999 --> 00:55:36,899
Having the freedom to write
About the things you love

1373
00:55:36,901 --> 00:55:38,271
Sounds like the perfect job.

1374
00:55:38,269 --> 00:55:39,699
So you're not angry?

1375
00:55:39,704 --> 00:55:44,044
I hope whatever you do next
Makes you happy.

1376
00:55:46,076 --> 00:55:48,136
Thank you for everything.

1377
00:55:48,145 --> 00:55:50,275
Don't suppose i could

1378
00:55:50,281 --> 00:55:52,011
Talk you into
Showing your gratitude

1379
00:55:52,016 --> 00:55:53,216
By giving me an article

1380
00:55:53,217 --> 00:55:54,747
On the gabriel august
Reveal tonight?

1381
00:55:54,752 --> 00:55:56,252
I can't.

1382
00:55:56,253 --> 00:55:59,253
I'm already covering it
For my own website.

1383
00:56:00,757 --> 00:56:03,287
[♪♪]

1384
00:56:04,461 --> 00:56:05,791
Call sophie.

1385
00:56:05,796 --> 00:56:07,096
[phone dialing]

1386
00:56:07,098 --> 00:56:08,598
[recording]: it's sophie.

1387
00:56:08,599 --> 00:56:10,799
Tell me what's on your mind
After the tone.

1388
00:56:10,801 --> 00:56:11,801
[phone beeps off]

1389
00:56:12,936 --> 00:56:15,336
[office bustling]

1390
00:56:29,252 --> 00:56:33,762
Hey. It's tabitha, right?

1391
00:56:33,758 --> 00:56:36,158
Hey, you kind of stood me
Up.

1392
00:56:36,160 --> 00:56:38,490
Actually, to be fair, i
Never
Said i was going to meet
You.

1393
00:56:38,496 --> 00:56:40,896
You work with
Sophie atkinson, right?

1394
00:56:40,898 --> 00:56:42,968
-you know sophie?
-yeah, is she here?

1395
00:56:42,967 --> 00:56:44,667
She was,
But she just quit.

1396
00:56:44,668 --> 00:56:46,798
Cleaned out her desk
About 20 minutes ago.

1397
00:56:46,804 --> 00:56:48,704
[groans] do you
Know where she went?

1398
00:56:48,706 --> 00:56:49,866
Jasper's.

1399
00:56:49,874 --> 00:56:52,414
To find out who gabriel
August really is.

1400
00:56:52,410 --> 00:56:54,580
Thanks.

1401
00:57:03,319 --> 00:57:05,819
Come on...

1402
00:57:05,823 --> 00:57:08,323
[quiet conversation]

1403
00:57:08,325 --> 00:57:10,625
[♪♪]

1404
00:57:19,936 --> 00:57:22,936
[horns honking]

1405
00:57:22,940 --> 00:57:25,110
Come on.

1406
00:57:25,109 --> 00:57:26,039
[phone chimes]

1407
00:57:29,279 --> 00:57:30,679
No.

1408
00:57:34,417 --> 00:57:36,147
Call jackie.

1409
00:57:36,153 --> 00:57:38,193
[phone ringing]

1410
00:57:38,189 --> 00:57:39,959
Where are you?

1411
00:57:39,957 --> 00:57:41,717
I'm on my way.

1412
00:57:41,725 --> 00:57:43,025
Meet me at the back door
Of the bookstore in 5
Minutes.

1413
00:57:43,027 --> 00:57:44,027
Okay.

1414
00:57:44,028 --> 00:57:45,988
[♪♪]

1415
00:57:59,008 --> 00:58:00,178
What is going on?

1416
00:58:00,177 --> 00:58:01,307
I can't go through with it.

1417
00:58:01,312 --> 00:58:03,082
-why?
-because she's here.

1418
00:58:03,080 --> 00:58:04,410
Oh, you didn't tell her yet?

1419
00:58:04,415 --> 00:58:07,215
I tried. I called, i texted,
I went to her work.

1420
00:58:07,218 --> 00:58:08,948
She's out there.

1421
00:58:08,953 --> 00:58:10,223
I can't let her find out
Along with everyone else.

1422
00:58:10,221 --> 00:58:12,421
Take a deep breath.
I will handle this.

1423
00:58:12,423 --> 00:58:14,523
Stay here.

1424
00:58:16,392 --> 00:58:18,262
Hello, sophie.

1425
00:58:18,262 --> 00:58:20,662
Hi, jackie!

1426
00:58:20,664 --> 00:58:22,504
How exciting is this?

1427
00:58:22,500 --> 00:58:23,500
Yeah, very,

1428
00:58:23,501 --> 00:58:24,701
And a little
Terrifying too.

1429
00:58:24,702 --> 00:58:26,972
I can imagine.

1430
00:58:26,971 --> 00:58:29,441
Is he going to show this
Time?

1431
00:58:29,440 --> 00:58:30,510
He's already here.

1432
00:58:30,508 --> 00:58:32,068
It's really happening, then?

1433
00:58:34,043 --> 00:58:37,113
Oh, i'm presuming you're
Here
To cover this for your
Paper?

1434
00:58:37,114 --> 00:58:38,754
Not exactly.

1435
00:58:38,749 --> 00:58:41,079
I'm not
With the daily anymore.

1436
00:58:41,085 --> 00:58:42,475
I'm actually here

1437
00:58:42,486 --> 00:58:44,386
Covering it
For my own website,

1438
00:58:44,388 --> 00:58:45,818
Which just went online.

1439
00:58:45,823 --> 00:58:47,523
Congratulations.

1440
00:58:47,525 --> 00:58:50,185
You let me know if i
Can help in any way.

1441
00:58:50,194 --> 00:58:51,564
Thanks.

1442
00:58:51,562 --> 00:58:54,202
I may hold you
To that.

1443
00:58:54,198 --> 00:58:55,728
In fact, um...

1444
00:58:55,733 --> 00:58:59,203
How would you like to
Scoop your old paper?

1445
00:58:59,203 --> 00:59:02,643
What are we talking,
Exactly?

1446
00:59:02,640 --> 00:59:04,510
Um, how about

1447
00:59:04,508 --> 00:59:08,038
The first real
Exclusive interview

1448
00:59:08,045 --> 00:59:10,245
With the real
Gabriel august himself?

1449
00:59:11,681 --> 00:59:13,751
Never meant to mislead
You...

1450
00:59:13,751 --> 00:59:16,081
I hope that we can--

1451
00:59:17,120 --> 00:59:18,790
Liam?

1452
00:59:18,789 --> 00:59:19,919
What are you
Doing here?

1453
00:59:19,924 --> 00:59:21,624
Oh, my gosh. You are
Not gonna believe--

1454
00:59:21,625 --> 00:59:24,155
Gabriel august
Will be here any minute

1455
00:59:24,161 --> 00:59:25,291
To chat with me.

1456
00:59:25,296 --> 00:59:26,556
Jackie got me
An exclusive!

1457
00:59:26,564 --> 00:59:28,134
I'll be quick.

1458
00:59:28,132 --> 00:59:29,362
I just need to say

1459
00:59:29,366 --> 00:59:31,626
What i wanted
To tell you earlier.

1460
00:59:31,635 --> 00:59:33,535
Actually, it's what
I've wanted to tell you

1461
00:59:33,537 --> 00:59:34,537
For a long time.

1462
00:59:34,538 --> 00:59:36,808
Liam, what--
What's going on?

1463
00:59:36,807 --> 00:59:38,367
You're the first thing
On my mind

1464
00:59:38,375 --> 00:59:40,635
When i wake up in the
Morning,

1465
00:59:40,644 --> 00:59:43,214
And the last thing i think
About
When i go to sleep,

1466
00:59:43,213 --> 00:59:45,713
And you're in there
A lot in between, too.

1467
00:59:45,716 --> 00:59:48,646
So, um, although it's...

1468
00:59:48,652 --> 00:59:51,422
Way past the time
I should have told you this,

1469
00:59:51,422 --> 00:59:53,962
Here it goes.

1470
00:59:53,958 --> 00:59:55,288
That crowd is here for me.

1471
00:59:57,026 --> 00:59:59,256
For you?

1472
01:00:00,129 --> 01:00:01,429
I'm gabriel august.

1473
01:00:01,432 --> 01:00:02,832
[laughs]

1474
01:00:02,833 --> 01:00:05,733
And i'm j.k. Rowling.
Nice to meet you.

1475
01:00:05,736 --> 01:00:07,936
[jackie]: we don't want to
Keep you waiting in suspense

1476
01:00:07,938 --> 01:00:09,368
Any longer.

1477
01:00:09,373 --> 01:00:11,643
Ladies and gentlemen,
In a minute,

1478
01:00:11,642 --> 01:00:14,242
It will be my pleasure
To introduce to you,

1479
01:00:14,244 --> 01:00:16,514
For the very first time,

1480
01:00:16,513 --> 01:00:19,453
The real man
Behind gabriel august.

1481
01:00:19,450 --> 01:00:20,820
I'm sorry.

1482
01:00:20,818 --> 01:00:23,588
I didn't want you
To find out this way.

1483
01:00:23,587 --> 01:00:26,687
That's crazy to hear.

1484
01:00:26,690 --> 01:00:27,690
You're serious.

1485
01:00:27,691 --> 01:00:29,421
I wanted to tell you before.

1486
01:00:29,426 --> 01:00:30,556
I should have.

1487
01:00:30,561 --> 01:00:32,161
I never meant to hurt you.

1488
01:00:32,162 --> 01:00:33,232
I promise.

1489
01:00:33,230 --> 01:00:34,260
How could i
Have missed this?

1490
01:00:34,264 --> 01:00:35,234
Sophie, please.

1491
01:00:35,232 --> 01:00:37,232
I can't do this.

1492
01:00:37,234 --> 01:00:38,404
No, please,
Just let me explain.

1493
01:00:38,402 --> 01:00:39,942
Please talk to me.

1494
01:00:39,937 --> 01:00:41,037
Wait!

1495
01:00:41,038 --> 01:00:43,208
Sophie, i love you.

1496
01:00:45,341 --> 01:00:47,141
I need to leave.

1497
01:00:47,144 --> 01:00:48,814
I wanted to tell you.
I swear.

1498
01:00:48,812 --> 01:00:50,912
Here he is... Liam bradley!

1499
01:00:50,914 --> 01:00:55,554
[applause]

1500
01:00:55,552 --> 01:00:58,892
I can't believe
I let this happen again.

1501
01:01:02,058 --> 01:01:04,588
[♪♪]

1502
01:01:13,803 --> 01:01:16,513
[applause continues]

1503
01:01:23,813 --> 01:01:26,823
[♪♪]

1504
01:01:35,958 --> 01:01:41,498
♪ seems you're a magnet
For tragedy ♪

1505
01:01:41,498 --> 01:01:44,428
♪ a vulnerable heart
That shaped who you are ♪

1506
01:01:44,435 --> 01:01:47,535
♪ a masterpiece

1507
01:01:47,538 --> 01:01:51,408
♪ cracks on the canvas
The lines on the face ♪

1508
01:01:51,408 --> 01:01:54,608
♪ the only hint

1509
01:01:54,611 --> 01:01:58,381
♪ the only trace of the
Hurt
That happened to you ♪

1510
01:02:00,316 --> 01:02:03,246
♪ that happened to you

1511
01:02:03,253 --> 01:02:05,193
♪ can't sleep

1512
01:02:05,189 --> 01:02:09,259
♪ can't keep him
From coming in the back
Door ♪

1513
01:02:09,259 --> 01:02:12,459
♪ board up the heart
And bag up the tears ♪

1514
01:02:12,463 --> 01:02:14,033
♪ and bury them

1515
01:02:15,865 --> 01:02:18,195
♪ yeah, you're walking on
Air

1516
01:02:18,202 --> 01:02:21,872
♪ numb to my touch

1517
01:02:21,872 --> 01:02:26,442
♪ how long have we been
In darkness? ♪

1518
01:02:42,492 --> 01:02:44,632
So, sophie,
How are you holding up?

1519
01:02:44,628 --> 01:02:46,328
I'm fine.

1520
01:02:46,330 --> 01:02:47,560
Really.

1521
01:02:47,564 --> 01:02:48,904
So you keep saying.

1522
01:02:48,899 --> 01:02:52,369
The new website is
Keeping me super busy.

1523
01:02:52,369 --> 01:02:54,539
I still can't believe
He was lying to you

1524
01:02:54,538 --> 01:02:55,668
All that time.

1525
01:02:55,672 --> 01:02:57,942
I can't believe
I didn't see it.

1526
01:02:57,941 --> 01:03:01,141
I mean, i told the guy
About lola.

1527
01:03:01,145 --> 01:03:03,975
You don't think he'll put
That
In some book one day, do
You?

1528
01:03:03,981 --> 01:03:06,181
He's probably forgotten
About us already.

1529
01:03:06,183 --> 01:03:10,123
He's got plenty
To keep him busy these days.

1530
01:03:10,120 --> 01:03:11,890
I'm not saying
That what he did was okay,

1531
01:03:11,889 --> 01:03:14,719
But i can sort of understand
It,
Given the circumstances.

1532
01:03:14,725 --> 01:03:15,885
Honey, you can't
Be serious.

1533
01:03:15,893 --> 01:03:17,363
For all we know,

1534
01:03:17,361 --> 01:03:18,431
He was just using her
To get a good review.

1535
01:03:18,428 --> 01:03:19,858
[nina]:
Or maybe he wanted her

1536
01:03:19,863 --> 01:03:21,263
To get to know him
As a normal person,

1537
01:03:21,265 --> 01:03:22,855
Not some celebrity author.

1538
01:03:22,866 --> 01:03:24,796
I-i don't know
What to say.

1539
01:03:24,802 --> 01:03:27,002
I really liked liam.

1540
01:03:27,004 --> 01:03:29,374
Not too often
I'm wrong about people.

1541
01:03:29,373 --> 01:03:31,813
It's not your fault.

1542
01:03:31,809 --> 01:03:33,539
It's nobody's fault
But my own.

1543
01:03:33,544 --> 01:03:36,984
I'll bring you a slice
Of lola's cobbler.

1544
01:03:36,980 --> 01:03:39,680
That always makes things
A little better.

1545
01:03:39,683 --> 01:03:41,023
Thanks.

1546
01:03:42,418 --> 01:03:43,718
Look.

1547
01:03:43,720 --> 01:03:45,390
I know it's been
Really rough,

1548
01:03:45,389 --> 01:03:46,959
And if i were in
The same place,

1549
01:03:46,957 --> 01:03:48,687
I can't say that
I'd feel any differently,

1550
01:03:48,692 --> 01:03:50,492
But it's hard for me
To believe

1551
01:03:50,494 --> 01:03:52,294
That he didn't truly
Care about you.

1552
01:03:52,296 --> 01:03:56,866
I'm not sure
What to think anymore.

1553
01:03:56,867 --> 01:03:59,297
But i do know one thing.

1554
01:03:59,303 --> 01:04:01,803
I can't go back to this.

1555
01:04:06,642 --> 01:04:08,542
Whatever we had,

1556
01:04:08,545 --> 01:04:11,375
It's over now.

1557
01:04:20,790 --> 01:04:23,290
[♪♪]

1558
01:04:59,862 --> 01:05:01,962
Hi.

1559
01:05:05,735 --> 01:05:08,365
I'm guessing this
Isn't a coincidence.

1560
01:05:08,372 --> 01:05:10,412
Well, i remember
You telling me

1561
01:05:10,407 --> 01:05:13,407
How much you love
Forest park.

1562
01:05:13,410 --> 01:05:15,610
That it was magical...

1563
01:05:15,612 --> 01:05:19,252
Your place to escape.

1564
01:05:19,249 --> 01:05:22,019
And...nina told me.

1565
01:05:22,019 --> 01:05:23,819
But don't blame her.

1566
01:05:23,820 --> 01:05:25,720
I called and practically
